72
00:05:11,125 --> 00:05:13,291
[sighs]

73
00:05:13,375 --> 00:05:15,916
[WORICK] See this is why
I don't trust cops.

74
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:18,375
Your work's even
dirtier than mine.

75
00:05:18,458 --> 00:05:20,541
[CHAD] It'd take the boys
in the crime lab forever

76
