the drug's use was prohibited
upon the war's end.

153
00:09:38,791 --> 00:09:40,166
I've learned it all.

154
00:09:40,250 --> 00:09:41,916
Don't bother coming in tomorrow.

155
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,625
That's not going to happen.

156
00:09:43,708 --> 00:09:46,541
Master Domenico hired me to
give you a proper education

157
00:09:46,625 --> 00:09:48,416
so the Arcangelo
family can maintain

158
00:09:48,500 --> 00:09:50,666
its sterling reputation.

159
