162
00:10:19,666 --> 00:10:21,375
[GASTON, WALLACE] I'm head
of the Westgate Mercenaries

163
00:10:21,458 --> 00:10:23,458
[WALLACE]
Captain Gaston Brown.

164
00:10:23,541 --> 00:10:24,958
