180
00:11:13,541 --> 00:11:16,208
[CHAD] Jesus, sounds like
a pretty rough battle.

181
00:11:16,291 --> 00:11:18,708
You sure you don't want
us to join in, too?

182
00:11:18,791 --> 00:11:21,250
[MONROE]
